### Squadbot
Squadbot is a modular whatsapp bot completely written in Node.js.

### Legal
Using whatsapp sockets is forbidden by their EULA. Squadbot has been created with the aim to learn more about bots, Reverse engineering and AI,
this means this repository can never be used for either commercial purposes, or educational purposes on a larger scale. For
these purposes you should consider using other protocols such as Telegram and IRC.


As stated in our License, we do not give any warranty, the Software and its source code is provided "AS IS".
Our license only includes our own code, the whatsapp code, logos and styles are copyrighted by Whatsapp inc.


We are not in any way associated with Whatsapp Inc. nor Facebook Inc. This isn't an official API!
